# Design System

> Source: `docs/design-system.md`, `docs/quality-bar.md`

## Tokens (mandatory)

| Token | Hex |
|-------|-----|
| primary | `#04324d` |
| accent | `#39a900` |

Never use `#1B2A4A` or ad-hoc colors.

## Every screen needs

Loading state | Empty state | Error with retry | One primary CTA

## Web

Reuse `.premium-table`, `.premium-card`, `.badge-base`, react-hook-form patterns in `client/src/index.css`.

## Mobile

Reuse `mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile/src/shared/ui/*` before new components.

## Language

Spanish (Colombia), institutional tone — AyudaTIC / MiAyudaTIC.

## Skill

Invoke `.cursor/skills/design-system` for UI workstreams.
